description:
Introducing the 2015 Subaru Legacy 2.5i Limited - the perfect combination of style, performance, and reliability. This sleek sedan is in immaculate condition, with only [insert number] miles on the odometer. With its spacious interior and impressive features, this vehicle is sure to exceed all your expectations.

The exterior of this Legacy is a stunning metallic silver, guaranteed to turn heads wherever you go. The aerodynamic design not only adds to its sleek appearance, but also improves fuel efficiency. Plus, with its all-wheel drive system, you can confidently tackle any terrain or weather condition.

Step inside and experience the luxurious and comfortable interior. The leather-trimmed seats provide ultimate comfort, while the heated front seats ensure you stay warm during those chilly winter months. The dual-zone automatic climate control allows you and your passengers to set individual temperature preferences for maximum comfort.

Equipped with a 2.5-liter four-cylinder engine, this Legacy delivers smooth and efficient performance. The continuously variable transmission (CVT) provides seamless shifting and improved fuel economy. Plus, with its advanced safety features such as blind spot detection and rearview camera, you can drive with peace of mind.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this 2015 Subaru Legacy 2.5i Limited. With its low mileage and exceptional features, it won't last long. Come in for a test drive today and experience the ultimate driving experience. This Legacy is waiting for you!

description:
Introducing the sleek and sophisticated 2015 Chrysler 200 Limited. This stunning sedan boasts a timeless design, with clean lines and a bold front grille. But don't let its striking appearance fool you, the 200 Limited is not just a pretty face.

Step inside and you'll be greeted with a spacious and luxurious interior. Premium cloth seats offer both comfort and style, while the Uconnect infotainment system keeps you connected on the go. With extra legroom and ample cargo space, you and your passengers can enjoy a comfortable ride every time.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful yet efficient 2.4-liter four-cylinder engine, delivering smooth and responsive performance. And with a 9-speed automatic transmission, the 200 Limited offers a seamless driving experience.

But that's not all, this 2015 Chrysler 200 Limited also comes equipped with advanced safety features such as electronic stability control, traction control, and an advanced airbag system, giving you peace of mind on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own this impressive sedan. Visit our showroom today and experience the 2015 Chrysler 200 Limited for yourself. With its spacious interior, efficient engine, and advanced safety features, it's the perfect blend of style and functionality. Don't wait, come in for a test drive and drive away in the car of your dreams.

Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and versatility in this 2015 Hyundai Elantra SE. With its sleek black exterior and well-appointed interior, this Elantra is a true standout in its class.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Elantra SE is equipped to enhance your driving experience. Key highlights include:

• LOCAL TRADE IN
• CARPETED FLOOR MATS

Under the hood, the Elantra's 1.8L I4 MPI DOHC 16V ULEV II engine delivers a responsive 145 horsepower, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic with Shiftronic transmission. With an EPA-estimated 28 MPG in the city and 38 MPG on the highway, this Elantra offers exceptional fuel efficiency to keep you on the road longer between fill-ups.

The interior of this Elantra SE is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Premium Cloth Seat Trim, a Tilt and Telescoping Steering Wheel, and a Rear Seat Center Armrest are just a few of the thoughtful amenities that make every journey a pleasure. Dual front airbags, ABS brakes, and Electronic Stability Control provide the peace of mind you deserve, while features like Cruise Control, Power Windows, and Remote Keyless Entry add to the overall driving experience.

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2015 Hyundai Elantra SE is up for the task. With its blend of style, efficiency, and well-appointed features, this Elantra is a smart choice for the savvy driver. We invite you to experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of owning this exceptional vehicle.

This spacious vehicle is perfect for daily commuting or long road trips, making it a versatile choice for any driver. Equipped with a 2.5L I4 engine, this Camry boasts an impressive 178 horsepower and 170ft. lbs. of torque, providing a smooth and responsive driving experience. Paired with a 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, this Camry offers effortless gear shifts and optimal fuel efficiency. Step inside and experience the luxurious and comfortable interior, complete with advanced features such as a multi-information display, Bluetooth connectivity, and a backup camera. With its low mileage and impeccable condition, this 2015 Toyota Camry is a must-see for anyone in the market for a reliable and stylish sedan. Don't miss out on this opportunity, visit us today and take this Camry for a test drive!

This 2015 Volkswagen Passat TDI SE is a low-mile diesel sedan that delivers exceptional fuel economy, smooth highway manners, and long-term durability. With only 116,817 miles, this Passat is a standout for anyone looking for an efficient, comfortable daily driver with proven diesel longevity.

Powered by Volkswagen’s TDI diesel engine, this Passat offers excellent torque and impressive highway range — making it ideal for commuting, road trips, or anyone who values efficiency without sacrificing performance. The diesel platform is well known for its ability to rack up miles while maintaining strong fuel economy.

The SE trim adds comfort and convenience features, including a refined interior, supportive seating, and user-friendly controls that make every drive enjoyable. The spacious cabin and large trunk give this sedan excellent practicality for both passengers and cargo.

If you’re looking for a clean, low-mile diesel sedan with outstanding fuel economy and a reputation for longevity, this 2015 Volkswagen Passat TDI SE is a smart choice.

description:
Celestial Silver Metallic 2015 Celestial Silver Metallic Toyota Camry CELESTIAL SILVER METALLIC Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

description:
Efficient, reliable, and beautifully maintained, this 2015 Toyota Corolla LE in Classic Silver Metallic delivers exceptional value and lasting quality. Known for its dependability and low cost of ownership, the Corolla LE remains one of the most trusted sedans on the road. Available now at Toyota of Portland, a CARFAX Top-Rated Dealer, this locally serviced Corolla shows meticulous care and attention from its previous owner.

According to CARFAX, this vehicle has been consistently serviced by Toyota of Portland's factory-trained technicians, including oil and filter changes, tire rotations, and a recent battery replacement in September 2025. With this history of professional care, you can drive with confidence knowing your Corolla has been maintained to Toyota's high standards.

Under the hood, the 1.8-liter Dual VVT-i 4-cylinder engine delivers smooth, efficient power through a continuously variable transmission (CVT). Combined with impressive fuel economy, the Corolla offers an effortless driving experience whether you're commuting through downtown Portland or exploring weekend getaways across the Pacific Northwest.

Inside, the LE trim offers thoughtful comfort and technology designed to make every drive more enjoyable. Standard features include a 6.1-inch touchscreen display, Bluetooth hands-free connectivity, backup camera, automatic climate control, and steering wheel-mounted controls for easy access to your favorite music and calls. Soft-touch materials, supportive cloth seats, and generous legroom create a refined and comfortable cabin environment.

Safety is at the heart of the Corolla's design, featuring Vehicle Stability Control, Traction Control, Anti-lock Brakes, and a suite of advanced airbags. Its high safety ratings and legendary Toyota reliability make this sedan a smart choice for anyone seeking confidence and long-term value.

Call (855) 685-1820 or visit toyotaofportland.com
to schedule your test drive at Toyota of Portland, 55 NE Broadway St, Portland, OR 97232. You'll enjoy transparent pricing, no dealer markups, and the award-winning service that has made us a CARFAX Top-Rated Dealer trusted by Oregon drivers.

Powered by a 3.7 Liter V6 that offers 328hp perfectly matched to a responsive 7 Speed Automatic transmission. This All Wheel Drive sedan results in brilliant driving dynamics highlighted by a composed and sure-footed ride with precise steering, strong acceleration, and nearly 26mpg on the open road! The classic elegance of our Q40 is complemented by attractive 17inch alloy wheels, a large sunroof, and automatic xenon headlights. Masterfully crafted with keen attention to detail to reward your senses, the Q40 interior greets you with sumptuous leather heated eight-way power front seats. Appreciate top-shelf amenities such as a 7-inch touch-screen infotainment system, full-color navigation, keyless ignition/entry, dual-zone automatic climate control, an auto-dimming rearview mirror, and a rear camera. Turn up the six-speaker sound system with a CD player, available satellite radio, and an iPod/USB interface, or stay connected via Bluetooth phone connectivity as you enjoy this first-class ride! Drive confidently with INFINITI as it offers Vehicle Dynamic Control, stability control, ABS, airbags, and intelligent All Wheel Drive with Snow mode. An ideal blend of power, style, comfort, and safety, this Q40 AWD Sedan is a compelling choice you've got to see first-hand! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

description: 2015 Toyota Corolla S Plus — Classic Silver Metallic exterior, Black cloth interior. Powered by the reliable 1.8L I4 engine producing 132 hp and 128 lb-ft of torque, this Corolla delivers responsive everyday performance with excellent fuel economy (EPA-estimated 28 MPG city / 37 MPG highway). Factory features and equipment (S Plus trim highlights): - Engine and chassis: 1.8L 4-cylinder engine tuned for efficiency and durability, standard stability and traction systems for confident handling. - Exterior sport styling: Sport front fascia and grille, body-color rear spoiler, fog lights, chrome-accent exhaust tip and 5-spoke alloy wheels that enhance the S-line appearance. - Lighting: Halogen projector headlamps with integrated turn indicators and front fog lamps for improved visibility. - Comfort and convenience: Black cloth sport seats with supportive bolstering, 60/40 split-folding rear seat, center console with armrest and storage, manual air-conditioning, power windows and door locks, remote keyless entry, and cruise control. - Driver interface: Tilt-and-telescoping steering column, easy-to-read instrumentation with tachometer and trip computer, steering-wheel mounted audio and phone controls for safe, convenient operation. - Infotainment and connectivity: Factory 6.1-inch touchscreen audio system (Entune-equipped on S Plus), Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming, USB and auxiliary inputs, AM/FM/CD, and available SiriusXM capability. Backup camera and integrated navigation were included on many S Plus-equipped examples. - Safety: Toyota’s comprehensive safety suite including ABS with Electronic Brake-force Distribution (EBD), Brake Assist, Vehicle Stability Control (VSC), Traction Control (TRAC), Smart Stop Technology, front and front-seat-mounted side airbags, full-length side curtain airbags, active headrests and Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). Condition and history: - Excellent overall condition inside and out. - Clean CARFAX report. - Below 96,000 miles total, averaging under 8,000 miles per year — a well-maintained, low-mileage example for its model year. This Corolla S Plus blends sporty styling with Toyota’s reputation for reliability and strong fuel economy, making it an excellent choice for commuting or everyday driving. Contact the dealership to confirm specific factory-installed options on this unit or to schedule a test drive.   • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane using countermeasures such as braking and/or steering. If the driver uses the turn signals, the system is temporarily disabled.
  • Steering assist and/or lane centering will maintain the vehicle's position within the lane with minimal input from the driver. The driver's hands must remain on the steering wheel, or touch the steering wheel every few seconds, for the system to remain active.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • Brake assist senses panic braking from the speed of the brake pedal's travel and applies all available power brake boost.

Trusted Name for 60+ Years Serving our community for over six decades with integrity, quality, & customer satisfaction The Hansel Auto Group story begins in 1851. Joseph Hansel first entered the transportation industry selling horse-drawn carriages. Joseph's son continued to build the Hansel name, opening the family's first automotive dealership in 1901. Hansel Auto Group first expanded into the Sonoma Valley in 1961 under the leadership of Walter Hansel. Walter believed that the Hansel name was about more than just selling cars. We are committed to giving back to our community. Walter Hansel partnered with multiple other local business owners to found what would become the local chapter of United Way. This began a long tradition of community involvement by the Hansel family.

description: Meet your new (but not actually new) best decision: a 2015 Hyundai Genesis 3.8L in a stunning Montecito Blue exterior with a Black leather interior — the kind of color combo that says “I care about style” without yelling about it. Powertrain & Performance - Factory 3.8L V6 delivering a hearty 311 hp and 293 ft-lbs of torque — enough shove to make you smile at stoplights. - Smooth-shifting automatic transmission (factory-calibrated for effortless highway passing and civilized cruising). - Real-world fuel economy: about 18 MPG city / 29 MPG highway — practical enough for daily life, peppy enough for the fun parts. Factory-Equipped Features (the good stuff that came from the factory, not aftermarket duct tape) - Luxurious Black leather seating straight from the factory — comfortable, classy, and easy to clean after life’s little spills. - Power-adjustable front seats with driver memory settings (factory convenience to stop the “where’d-I-leave-my-seat” squabble). - Heated front seats for those mornings that feel like the Arctic without warning. - Dual-zone automatic climate control so you and your passenger can wage tiny temperature wars independently. - Keyless entry and push-button start — because digging for keys is retro, and this car is not. - Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming, plus steering-wheel-mounted audio and cruise controls for safe, convenient command. - AM/FM audio with CD and auxiliary/USB connectivity — modern meets analog for your curated playlist library. - Automatic headlights and well-designed exterior lighting for improved visibility and that “look” on the road. - Comprehensive factory safety suite: ABS, traction and stability control, multiple airbags (front, side, curtain), and tire pressure monitoring — all the basics you want keeping you honest and upright. - Solid build quality and refined suspension tuning — this is a luxury sedan that behaves like one. Condition & History - Excellent overall condition inside and out — this Genesis has been well cared for and it shows. - Clean CARFAX report — no drama, no mystery, just a clean history. - Mileage is under 103,000 miles, averaging less than 9,000 miles per year — a sensible, low-mileage lifestyle for a vehicle this age. Why this one? If you want a grown-up luxury sedan that still has some pep, looks great in Montecito Blue, and won’t demand soul-searching at the pump, this Genesis is worth a look. It’s polished, practical, and just a little smug in the best way — like a sports coat with sneakers. Want to take it for a test-drive and confirm that the V6 is, in fact, an excellent conversational partner? description: Meet the 2015 BMW 750i — the kind of luxury sedan that makes your coffee taste hotter and your commute feel like First Class. Under the hood: a 4.4L Twin-Turbo V8 that delivers 445 horsepower and 480 lb-ft of torque, mated to a smooth 8-speed automatic transmission. It hustles when you want it to and relaxes when you don’t — 17 MPG city, 25 MPG highway, and surprisingly reasonable mileage for its class (under 86,000 miles total — that’s less than 8,000 miles per year on average). Eye candy and interior decadence - Exterior: Imperial Blue Metallic — deep, classy, and just the right amount of “I know what I’m doing.” - Interior: Ivory White and Black leather seating surfaces that contrast beautifully and feel like a private jet seat. Rich trim and tasteful chrome accents complete the executive vibe. - Comfort features include power-adjustable front seats with memory and lumbar support, premium leather upholstery, and a well-appointed cockpit that puts everything within reach. Factory-equipped luxury and tech (in plain English) - BMW iDrive infotainment system with generous display and rotary controller for navigation, audio, and vehicle settings — everything is where your brain expects it to be. - Factory navigation and voice control so your phone calls and directions don’t require interpretive dance. - Premium factory audio system to make your playlists sound like they had their own stylist. - Multi-zone automatic climate control so you and your passengers can wage a truce over temperature preferences. - Power sunroof/panoramic glass lets in just enough sky to feel worldly without ruining your hair. - Power trunk and keyless entry/start for when you’re hands-full or just dramatically approaching your car. - Adaptive driving modes (Comfort, Sport, Economy-minded options) so the car matches your mood — zen commuter or eager roadster. - Adaptive suspension and ride control that smooths out the road like a polite moderator at a heated meeting. - Parking sensors and back-up camera to save you from mailbox trauma. - Full complement of safety basics: ABS, traction and stability control, multiple airbags, and solid BMW engineering that has been doing this long enough to be smug about it. Condition & peace of mind - Excellent overall condition inside and out — this 7 Series was pampered. - SALVAGE CARFAX report ! - Low annual mileage for its age means more great years ahead. Why this one? If you want a flagship sedan that blends serious V8 power with living-room luxury and a hint of techy wizardry, this Imperial Blue 750i with Ivory/Black leather is essentially a four-wheeled velvet rope. It’s polished, powerful, and practical enough to be your daily driver — with the muscle to remind everyone at the light that you do mean business. Ready to meet your new commute’s new boss? Come take it for a spin and try not to grin too hard. 7 Star Auto Sales 5000 Madison Ave SACRAMENTO, CA 95841 (916) 545-2255 7 Star Auto Sales is a used car dealership located in Sacramento, CA, known for offering a wide selection of quality pre-owned vehicles. The dealership is focused on providing a transparent, fair, and hassle-free car-buying experience for its customers. description: Meet this pristine 2015 Lincoln MKZ (also known as the Zephyr in some circles) — finished in White Platinum Metallic Tri-Coat on the outside and wrapped in Light Dune leather on the inside. Under the hood is the punchy EcoBoost 2.0L Turbo I4, delivering a very respectable 240 hp and 270 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission and standard front-wheel drive (all-wheel drive was available on some trims), this MKZ brings surprising pep while still being sensible: it averages 22 MPG city and 33 MPG highway. With under 60,000 miles (that’s less than 5,000 miles per year), a clean CARFAX and excellent overall condition, this one is as close to a time capsule as a daily-driver luxury sedan gets — without the dust. Factory-standard features you’ll actually use (and appreciate) - Comfort and trim: Light Dune leather-trimmed seating, power-adjustable front seats with lumbar support, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel. Rear seats fold 60/40 to add practicality when you need it, so your grocery run or weekend IKEA conquest is covered. - Climate and convenience: Dual-zone automatic climate control keeps the driver and passenger from arguing over the thermostat. Power windows, power door locks, and remote keyless entry are standard, along with push-button start for that “luxury without the fuss” feeling. - Infotainment and connectivity: Lincoln’s infotainment system (SYNC/MyLincoln Touch era) with a central display provides Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming, USB and auxiliary inputs, and intuitive steering-wheel audio controls. AM/FM and satellite radio capability mean you’ll never be short on listening options. - Safety and driver aids: Built with a full suite of factory safety equipment — multiple airbags (front, side and curtain), anti-lock brakes (ABS), traction control and electronic stability control — the MKZ was designed to look after occupants. Rear-view camera and parking aids were offered to make parking less of a dramatic event. Advanced features like blind-spot monitoring, cross-traffic alert, adaptive cruise control or collision mitigation were available on higher trims/options. - Exterior and lighting: The White Platinum Metallic Tri-Coat finish gives the MKZ a refined, showroom-ready look. Factory exterior touches include power heated mirrors, halogen projector headlights (HID lighting was available on some packages), and stylish alloy wheels that complement the Lincoln grille and chrome accents. - Luxury add-ons often found on these models: sunroof/moonroof, adaptive suspension, upgraded premium audio (Revel by Harman on some units), navigation, and active park assist — handy if parallel parking gives you the willies. Why this one stands out (besides the color combo) - Low mileage: under 60,000 miles, averaging less than 5,000 miles per year — this MKZ has been lightly used and well cared for. - Clean CARFAX: no accidents or title issues — just straightforward, honest ownership history. - Excellent overall condition: cosmetically and mechanically ready to make a new owner very happy. If you want a luxury sedan that manages to be both composed and fun (without guzzling premium gas like it’s trying to impress someone), this MKZ is a smart, stylish pick. It’s the kind of car that says “I take my comfort seriously” but still enjoys getting up and going when you do — and with mileage this low, it’s got plenty of getting-up-and-going left. 7 Star Auto Sales 5000 Madison Ave SACRAMENTO, CA 95841 (916) 545-2255 7 Star Auto Sales is a used car dealership located in Sacramento, CA, known for offering a wide selection of quality pre-owned vehicles. The dealership is focused on providing a transparent, fair, and hassle-free car-buying experience for its customers. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance with this exceptional 2015 Nissan Altima 2.5 SV. This meticulously maintained sedan offers an unparalleled driving experience, packed with a host of premium features that will elevate your daily commute.

• Nissan Navigation System
• Front Passenger Window w/1-Touch Auto-Up/Down
• HomeLink Universal Transceiver
• Power Sliding Moonroof w/Tilt
• Blind Spot Warning
• Lane Departure Warning System
• Manual Folding Outside Mirrors
• Auto-Dimming Rear-View Mirror
• Compass
• Side Cargo Net

Beneath the sleek and sophisticated exterior, this Altima is powered by a 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine, delivering an impressive 27 city/38 highway MPG. The CVT with Xtronic transmission ensures a smooth and responsive ride, while the front-wheel-drive system provides confident handling in all driving conditions.

The Convenience Package adds a touch of luxury, with features like rear passenger A/C vents, a mood lamp in the roof console, and an auto-dimming rearview mirror. The Technology Package takes your driving experience to new heights, with advanced safety features like Moving Obstacle Detection, Blind Spot Warning, and Lane Departure Warning.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring high-quality materials and thoughtful design. The 7-inch color display with the Nissan Navigation System provides turn-by-turn directions, while the steering wheel-mounted controls allow you to seamlessly manage your audio and connectivity.

With its exceptional fuel efficiency, advanced safety technologies, and premium amenities, this 2015 Nissan Altima 2.5 SV is the perfect blend of practicality and sophistication. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the value and performance this Altima has to offer.

description:
The 2021 Nissan Altima SR offers exceptional value by packaging advanced tech and upscale features as standard, including a moonroof, 19-inch alloy wheels, heated front seats, and NissanConnect with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. At this price point, competitors often charge extra for similar equipment, making the Altima SR a smart money decision for maximizing feature content per dollar.

Analytical buyers who demand clear value will appreciate the Altima SR’s generous standard features, safety technologies, and sport-inspired design. Those who compare spec sheets will find the SR trim delivers upgraded wheels, power driver seat, and premium convenience without costly add-ons. This sedan appeals to shoppers wanting maximum equipment at a competitive ownership cost.

The Altima SR delivers solid performance with a fuel-efficient 2.5L engine mated to an Xtronic CVT, providing a strong balance of 188 horsepower and up to 34 highway mpg. This translates to real-world savings at the pump—averaging about 29 mpg combined—while maintaining responsive acceleration. Maintenance costs remain low due to Nissan’s proven powertrain reliability, protecting long-term value.

Safety value is a standout, as the Altima SR includes Blind Spot Warning, Rear Parking Sensors, Brake Assist, and multiple airbags as standard—features that are often optional on rivals. Electronic Stability Control, ABS, and automatic high-beam headlights further enhance on-road safety. These systems function seamlessly to help prevent collisions and increase driver confidence, all included in the base price.

Beyond core equipment, the Altima SR features a power moonroof, dual-zone climate control, sport steering wheel, and heated front seats, elevating comfort without requiring premium packages. SiriusXM, six speakers, and steering wheel audio controls ensure entertainment is standard. The trunk organizer tray and split-folding rear seats add flexible cargo utility, while the NissanConnect infotainment system offers easy smartphone integration.

When compared to the Toyota Camry SE and Honda Accord Sport, the Altima SR includes more standard safety tech and convenience features for the price. While others may require costly packages for heated seats or blind spot monitoring, this sedan delivers these features up front. The result is a better feature-to-price ratio, maximizing value without sacrificing quality or comfort.

Standard equipment in the Altima SR includes heated front seats, Blind Spot Warning, a power driver seat, and 19-inch wheels. This vehicle is worth the price due to its above-class standard content and efficient operation. The SR trim is the best value, as it combines sport styling and tech at no extra charge. While competitors charge extra for safety tech, here it's included as standard.

Bayway Chevrolet invites you to experience the Altima SR’s value in person. Visit us at 5719 Broadway St, Pearland, TX, 77581 or call 281-719-9821 to schedule your test drive and discover how you can maximize your investment without compromising on quality or features. Your smart money decision starts here.

Why BUY from J. Allen Toyota? When you choose this Satin Cashmere Metallic 2011 Lexus LS 460 SEDAN with 104,703 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Comfort
  • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
  • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

description: This 2011 Honda Civic LX Sedan is the definition of “simple, reliable, and cheap to own” — and that’s exactly why Civics have basically been the king of affordable daily drivers forever. It’s powered by Honda’s fuel-sipping 1.8L 4-cylinder paired with an automatic transmission, and since it’s FWD it’s easygoing in winter while still giving you great MPG for commuting. History-wise, it shows only 3 previous owners and 11 documented service history records, plus it’s exactly the kind of low-drama car that just starts every day, gets you where you’re going, and doesn’t ask for much in return. Inside, this LX trim is all about practicality done right — comfortable cloth seating, ice-cold A/C, a clean straightforward dash layout, and a trunk that’s honestly huge for how compact the car is. You also get the stuff people actually care about in a daily: power windows/locks, cruise control (major for highway driving), solid factory audio, and a driver-friendly seating position with excellent visibility. This is the perfect “first car,” “commuter,” or “work car” setup — light, easy to maneuver, and cheap on brakes/tires/gas compared to almost anything else. Price excludes tax, title, license, and service fee. Please contact dealer to verify all standard and optional equipment. This vehicle compares to Toyota Corolla, Mazda3, and Hyundai Elantra.

description:
Discover the exceptional value and impressive features of this 2011 Toyota Camry LE. With its sleek black exterior and well-appointed interior, this Camry delivers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and reliability that discerning drivers demand.

• Power windows, power locks, tilt wheel, and cruise control
• Remote keyless entry, traction control, and ABS brakes
• Low tire pressure warning and electronic stability control
• Illuminated entry

Beneath the hood, you'll find a robust 2.5L I4 SMPI DOHC engine paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed transmission, providing a rewarding and efficient driving experience. With an impressive 22 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, this Camry offers exceptional fuel economy to help you save at the pump.

Inside, the well-appointed cabin features a comprehensive array of amenities, including a premium audio system with CD player, air conditioning, and a power driver's seat. The spacious interior and split-folding rear seat provide ample room for passengers and cargo, ensuring your daily commute or weekend getaway is both comfortable and convenient.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an occupant sensing airbag system to help protect you and your loved ones. The four-wheel disc brakes, speed-sensing steering, and four-wheel independent suspension further enhance the Camry's driving dynamics and overall safety.

This 2011 Toyota Camry LE is a true testament to the brand's reputation for quality, durability, and value. With its impressive list of features and proven reliability, it's an exceptional choice for the discerning driver. Visit our showroom today and experience the exceptional value and performance of this remarkable Camry for yourself.

The A8 L's interior is crafted with premium materials, including plush leather seats and wood accents, creating a refined and upscale atmosphere. The spacious cabin provides ample legroom and headroom, ensuring that all occupants are comfortable during long drives.

Equipped with advanced features such as a navigation system, Bluetooth connectivity, and a premium sound system, the A8 L offers convenience and entertainment at your fingertips. Safety is also a top priority, with features like adaptive cruise control, blind-spot monitoring, and a rearview camera, giving you peace of mind on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own this stunning 2011 Audi A8 L quattro. With its luxurious interior, powerful performance, and advanced technology, this sedan is the epitome of elegance and sophistication. Stop by our dealership and take a test drive today!

description: The 2011 BMW 335i xDrive is the kind of sport sedan that reminds you why BMW owned this segment for so long. Under the hood lives the brand’s signature turbocharged inline-six, an engine that delivers a deep well of torque, silk-smooth power delivery, and that unmistakable BMW growl when you lean into the throttle. Paired with the automatic transmission and BMW’s xDrive all-wheel-drive system, it puts its power down confidently in all seasons without dulling the car’s athletic edge. On the road, the 335i still feels purpose-built. Steering is precise, the chassis feels balanced and planted, and the suspension strikes that classic BMW compromise—firm enough to entertain, compliant enough to live with every day. Alloy wheels fill the arches just right, giving the car a stance that’s sporty without trying too hard. Inside, it’s a familiar BMW formula done well. Supportive seats with heating add everyday comfort, the driving position is spot-on, and everything falls naturally to hand. It’s a cockpit designed for people who actually enjoy driving, not just commuting. This example sweetens the deal with a clean CarFax and just 77,000 miles, refreshingly low for a car that was engineered to rack up many more. In a world increasingly dominated by numb crossovers and overstyled tech showcases, the 2011 335i xDrive stands out as a genuinely engaging, premium sport sedan that still knows what it’s supposed to be.

What is Wholesale Open to Public? Derrow Shirkey Ford's Wholesale Open to Public is a select offering of used cars that have traditionally been sold at the auction to independent dealers and small used car lots. These are vehicles that fall outside of Derrow Shirkey Ford's used car guidelines. They are generally higher mileage, older, lower-priced vehicles that are perhaps 'flawed' in some way. Some general guidelines for a wholesale vehicle: • They are sold without a warranty • They are offered for a limited time only - 30 days • They are sold 100% AS-IS without any warranty coverage • They are sold with our "best price" posted on the windshield. There is no negotiation necessary. Why Wholesale Open to Public? Simply put - our customers have requested that we make these vehicles available. Many of our customers have a need for basic transportation. By offering a broader selection of "kid's cars", 2nd car, college cars, and other inexpensive transportation options, we feel we can better serve our current customers and the general market.

We are located 2 miles South of the turnpike at exit 13. Our location makes it a very simple drive from Toledo, Fort Wayne, Hillsdale, Angola, Bryan, Defiance, Napoleon, or Jackson. OUR MISSION STATEMENT- We will be honest and transparent. Through teamwork, honesty and hard work, we will build trusting relationships with our customers, always striving to exceed their expectations. The same holds true for our team members as we constantly learn and improve from within ourselves and each other. Come see for yourself why Derrow-Shirkey Ford Lincoln is the fastest growing dealership in the tri-state area. We are committed to making the car buying experience fast, fun and easy!!! 1. Pricing - We post our best price on every vehicle, every day. Period. 2. Trade In’s - We’ll make you a cash offer. No-Nonsense. We will buy your vehicle regardless if you purchase from us or not. 3. Financing - Multiple quotes in minutes. 4. No Surprises - We will gladly provide a history report and a copy of any repairs we performed on the vehicle. 5. Long Distance, No Problem! - We sell vehicles from New York to California.

description: This 2011 Ford Taurus SEL is the kind of full-size sedan that just makes sense — smooth, comfortable, roomy, and way more loaded than most people expect. It’s powered by the proven 3.5L V6 paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, giving it that effortless highway power and the classic Taurus ride quality that feels stable, quiet, and confident at any speed. And this one checks the big boxes buyers actually care about: the CARFAX shows a 1-owner, clean history with no accidents, plus documented service records including a recent oil & filter change. Even better, the CARFAX Reliability Forecast rates it as “Good Reliability” compared to similar vehicles, citing regular oil changes and strong long-term ownership expectations — which is exactly what you want backing up a daily-driver sedan like this. Inside, this Taurus is genuinely loaded — like surprisingly loaded. The Rapid Spec 202A (SYNC voice-activated system, Sony premium audio system w/12 speakers, rear view camera, reverse sensing system, push-button start, ambient interior lighting, power adjustable pedals) gives you a big chunk of the “modern car” experience without the modern car payment. Add in heated leather seating and a power moonroof, and it ends up feeling way more upscale than most sedans in this price range. Everything is laid out nicely, easy to use, and the cabin has that comfortable, quiet Taurus feel that makes you want to keep driving instead of rushing to park it. Price excludes tax, title, license, and service fee. Please contact dealer to verify all standard and optional equipment. This vehicle compares to Chevrolet Impala, Toyota Avalon, and Hyundai Azera.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2020 Toyota Corolla SE. This stunning sedan boasts a captivating Red exterior and a host of premium features that will exceed your expectations.

• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio data system
• Radio: Audio AM/FM w/Navigation
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Rear window defroster
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls

Powered by a 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V engine paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, this Corolla SE delivers an impressive balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 31 city/40 highway mpg. Its well-appointed interior and advanced safety technologies provide a refined and confident driving experience.

Indulge in the convenience of features like the Exterior Parking Camera Rear, Auto High-beam Headlights, and the intuitive Apple CarPlay integration. The Corolla SE's premium Fabric Seat Trim and 18" Machined Alloy Wheels add a touch of sophistication to every journey.

Safety is paramount, and this Corolla SE is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, Brake Assist, and Electronic Stability Control, ensuring your peace of mind on the road.

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, this 2020 Toyota Corolla SE is the perfect companion. Its blend of style, technology, and performance make it a standout in its class. Visit our showroom today to experience the Corolla SE for yourself and discover why it's the smart choice for your next vehicle.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2020 Ford Fusion Titanium, a sophisticated and well-equipped sedan that offers a dynamic driving experience. With its sleek black exterior and a powerful EcoBoost 2.0L I4 GTDi DOHC Turbocharged VCT engine, this Fusion Titanium is a true standout in its class.

Key features include:
• Navigation System
• 12 Speakers
• SiriusXM Radio
• SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System
• Leather Heated/Cooled Sport Bucket Seats
• Ventilated Front Seats
• Power Moonroof
• 19" Machined-Face Aluminum Wheels

This Fusion Titanium is more than just a stylish ride, it's a testament to Ford's commitment to innovation and technology. The SYNC 3 system seamlessly integrates your smartphone, allowing you to access your favorite apps, make hands-free calls, and navigate with ease. The premium audio system from Sony will immerse you in your music, while the leather-wrapped, heated and ventilated seats provide unparalleled comfort.

Elevate your driving experience with the power and precision of the Fusion Titanium's all-wheel-drive system. Tackle any road with confidence, thanks to the vehicle's responsive handling and the added traction of AWD. And with an impressive fuel economy of 20 city/29 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of performance and efficiency.

Beyond its dynamic capabilities, the Fusion Titanium offers a wealth of advanced safety features, including a Rear View Camera, Blind Spot Monitoring, and a suite of airbags to keep you and your passengers secure. The automatic high-beam headlights and rain-sensing wipers add an extra layer of convenience, ensuring you're always prepared for any driving conditions.

This 2020 Ford Fusion Titanium represents an exceptional value at just $11,981. With its impressive list of features, powerful engine, and exceptional safety ratings, it's a must-see for any discerning buyer. Visit our showroom today to experience the Fusion Titanium for yourself and discover why it's the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

We buy quality well maintained vehicles. (Local individuals & Franchise auctions)We avoid vehilces that have bad reliability ratings. Even though a lot of those vehicles are profitable, we still avoid them like the plague except on super rare occasions. For example, you will never see Hyundai, Kia, Nissans 2019 or older (Bad transmissions), Chevy Traverse/GMC Acadia (Most model years), Poorly maintained BMWs, AUDIs, RANGE ROVERs, etc. We simply refuse to sell vehicles that are likely to be a bad investment for our clients. If, on rare occasion we take one on trade we list it because we feel strongly about its quality and we will most definitely recommend our warranty partner AUL (One of the best warranty companies nationwide)We have certified and highly experienced mechanics that carefully inspect, road test and service our vehicles. We don't just wash them and put them for sale. We genuinly do our best to give you true quality. We spend a fortune on gas to drive our vehicles for 50 to 100 even 200 miles if we have to to make sure we complete 2 drive cycles before we get a 3rd party state inspection station to inspect them. Warranty is nice but doesn't work if anything happens in the first 30 days, no worries. We are very transparent with our agreements so as long as we did not already disclose it or agree on it prior to the sale and you some how despite of everything we did still get a check engine light, your AC stops working for example or transmmission goes out (One in a million chance) we still got your back. If the deal qualifies for the our 30 day gaurantee then we will take care of you.Much more to list, just know that once you join the family you will never shop anywhere else. *The advertised down payments are meant to be a rough estimate because it's the #1 question everyone calls about. You never know what it is until you speak with us, we chat about it to figure out your unique situation and finally fillout a credit application for us to geniunly shop you the best possible deal Call us, it won't take long, we promise.

description: At Premier Automotive Inc., one of the largest pre-owned car dealerships in the DMV area, we proudly offer over 300 vehicles in stock, providing a wide selection for our customers. Speak with your salesperson about our special warranty options to ensure you get the most protection for your vehicle.Recall & Manufacturer Warranty DisclaimerPremier Automotive Inc. is not responsible for any open recalls. We encourage all customers to check for active recalls by visiting nhtsa.gov/recalls. Additionally, we cannot be held liable for manufacturer warranties that may be voided due to previous accidents, damages, auction disclosures, or lack of maintenance by prior owners.Pricing, Fees, and Availability DisclaimerAll vehicle prices are subject to change without prior notice based on market conditions, demand, and availability. We reserve the right to remove listings at any time if a vehicle is sold or otherwise no longer available. The price listed on our website at the time of purchase is the final selling price and supersedes any previously advertised prices. Previously advertised prices will not be honored once updated. While we strive to ensure accurate pricing, we are not responsible for typographical errors, pricing discrepancies, or delays in updating online listings. We are not responsible for outdated pricing or inaccurate vehicle information displayed on external websites. The most accurate and up-to-date pricing and availability can always be found directly on our official dealership website. Prices and promotions on third-party sites do not control or dictate dealership pricing. Customers should verify all pricing details with us directly before making a purchase decision.

Why we use market based pricing?


We believe that today's used car buyers search the Internet to find the best value on the vehicle they want. Each search returns dozens, if not hundreds, of similar vehicles in their area to consider. Customers shorten this to a manageable list by ranking vehicles with the best price and mileage at the top. Because of this we utilize a software tool that show us where our inventory ranks on popular car shopping sites when searched and gives us the information we need to immediately adjust our prices and drive customers to our lot. We believe that Market Based Pricing aligns our cars best with what the consumer is looking for.

Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance in this 2020 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S. This sleek and sophisticated sedan offers an exceptional driving experience, packed with a host of advanced features that cater to your every need.

Elevate your commute with the impressive array of premium upgrades, including:

• Driver Assistance Package, featuring Blind Spot Monitor with Rear Traffic Alert, Forward Collision Warning, and autonomous emergency braking (Front Assist)
• MojoMats with Logo Carpeted Mats (Set of 4)

The Jetta's 1.4L TSI engine, paired with a smooth 6-speed manual transmission, delivers an exhilarating and efficient ride, with an impressive 30 city/40 highway MPG. Enjoy the confidence of front-wheel drive and the responsiveness of speed-sensing steering, making every journey a pleasure.

Step inside and experience the Jetta's refined interior, where the cloth seat trim and front bucket seats provide exceptional comfort. Stay connected with the Composition Color touchscreen infotainment system, which seamlessly integrates with your smartphone via VW App-Connect, offering Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and MirrorLink capabilities.

Safety is a top priority, and the Jetta is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance features. Enjoy the added security of dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an emergency communication system with VW Car-Net services.

Beyond its impressive performance and technology, the Jetta's sleek exterior design exudes a sense of sophistication. The body-color bumpers, 16-inch silver-painted alloy wheels, and fully automatic headlights contribute to its modern and refined appearance.

This 2020 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S is the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency, offering an unparalleled driving experience. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional sedan for a test drive and discover how it can elevate your daily commute.

This vehicle is located at Gates Chevrolet in South Bend 311 E Ireland rd. South Bend, IN 46614.... Call/text 574-387-2541 for more info.

This 2020 Ford Fusion SE is a remarkable value, packed with premium features that will elevate your driving experience. Let's take a closer look at what this exceptional sedan has to offer:

• CUSTOMER FOR LIFE WARRANTY-ASK ABOUT IT! GATES HAS YOUR BACK!
• FORD CO-PILOT360 ASSIST: Voice-Activated Touchscreen Navigation System, pinch-to-zoom capability, SiriusXM Traffic and Travel Link, Adaptive Cruise Control w/Stop & Go
• POWER MOONROOF

With its sleek gray exterior and well-appointed interior, this Fusion SE delivers a sophisticated and modern aesthetic. The 1.5L EcoBoost engine and 6-speed automatic transmission provide a smooth and efficient driving experience, while the front-wheel-drive configuration ensures confident handling in a variety of road conditions.

Fuel efficiency is a top priority, and this Fusion SE delivers an impressive 23 MPG in the city and 34 MPG on the highway, making it an excellent choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

The Ford Co-Pilot360 Assist suite of advanced safety and driver-assistance technologies, including Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go, will give you peace of mind on the road. The voice-activated touchscreen navigation system and SiriusXM radio will keep you connected and entertained throughout your journey.

Step inside the Fusion SE and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin. Cloth front bucket seats provide all-day comfort, while the power driver's seat and tilt/telescoping steering wheel allow you to find your perfect driving position. The rear seats offer ample room for passengers, and the split-folding design provides versatility for your cargo needs.

This Fusion SE is an exceptional value, with a long list of premium features and a low mileage of just 100,982 miles. At Gates Chevrolet, we're committed to providing our customers with top-quality vehicles and unparalleled service.

Don't miss your opportunity to experience the 2020 Ford Fusion SE for yourself. Stop by our showroom or give us a call to schedule a test drive today. We look forward to helping you find the perfect vehicle for your needs.

description: Meet the 2010 Cadillac CTS 3.0L V6 Luxury — the kind of car that politely corrects your posture and your playlist at the same time. Radiant Silver on the outside (yes, it still turns heads), and wrapped in Titanium leather with Ebony accents on the inside — which reads like “executive chair” but drives like “weekend escape.” Under the hood sits the smooth 3.0L V6 producing a healthy 270 hp and 223 lb-ft of torque, delivering confident passing power and a poised, comfortable ride. This CTS is in excellent overall condition, has a clean CARFAX, and has been gently used — under 121,000 miles, averaging less than 8,000 miles per year. Fuel economy is a friendly 18 MPG city / 27 MPG highway, so you can feel fancy without constantly visiting the pump. Factory-equipped features (yes, the good stuff built in from the start) - Premium leather interior: Full Titanium leather seating with elegant Ebony accents — soft, supportive, and ready for whatever your commute throws at it. - Comfort and seating: Power-adjustable front seats with supportive bolstering and lumbar adjustment for long-trip comfort. Heated front seats help keep the chill out and the smiles in. - Climate control: Dual-zone automatic climate control so driver and passenger can wage a silent battle over temperature without touching the radio. - Audio and connectivity: Factory premium audio system (Bose-equipped on Luxury trims) delivering crisp, room-filling sound, AM/FM/CD with auxiliary input and XM satellite radio capability — your playlists finally deserve premium treatment. Hands-free calling and audio streaming through factory Bluetooth (and OnStar capability) make multitasking safe and civilized. - Convenience features: Remote keyless entry and power door locks/windows/mirrors, steering-wheel-mounted audio and cruise controls for on-the-fly convenience, a thoughtfully designed center console and storage that actually holds more than you think. - Exterior and lighting: Radiant Silver paint with sharp body lines and Cadillac’s signature grille — confident looks that don’t try too hard. Fog lamps and projector-style headlights provide excellent nighttime visibility and curb appeal. - Wheels and brakes: Factory alloy wheels wrapped in good-condition tires, with four-wheel antilock brakes (ABS) offering strong, predictable stopping power. - Safety and security: A full complement of airbags (front, side-impact, and side curtain), traction control and stability control systems to help keep things orderly, tire pressure monitoring, and factory-installed OnStar emergency/assistance features to add that extra peace of mind. - Build quality and refinement: Solid fit and finish, quiet cabin insulation, and Cadillac’s characteristic blend of athletic handling and luxury ride quality — designed to make every trip feel a little more special. Why this CTS? Because it’s the kind of car that quietly impresses. Refined styling, real V6 power, comfortable leather interior, and thoughtful creature comforts — all with low average annual mileage, a clean CARFAX, and excellent overall condition. It’s a luxury sedan that behaves responsibly and still knows how to enjoy the road. Bring your sense of adventure (and maybe a favorite playlist). This Radiant Silver CTS is ready to make your driveway look better and your commute a little more dignified — with a wink. 7 Star Auto Sales 5000 Madison Ave SACRAMENTO, CA 95841 (916) 545-2255 7 Star Auto Sales is a used car dealership located in Sacramento, CA, known for offering a wide selection of quality pre-owned vehicles. The dealership is focused on providing a transparent, fair, and hassle-free car-buying experience for its customers. description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology in this stunning 2017 Honda Accord EX-L. With its sleek black exterior and meticulously crafted interior, this Accord is a true testament to Honda's commitment to excellence.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Accord is equipped to elevate your driving experience. Highlights include:

• Remote keyless entry
• Power driver's seat with memory function
• Dual-zone automatic climate control
• Leather-trimmed seats
• Heated front seats
• Power moonroof
• 360-Watt premium audio system
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration
• Rearview camera with dynamic guidelines
• Honda Sensing® suite of advanced safety technologies

The Accord's 2.4L I4 DOHC i-VTEC engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, delivers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 27 mpg in the city and 36 mpg on the highway. This combination ensures you'll enjoy a rewarding and economical driving experience, no matter the road ahead.

Complementing the Accord's impressive performance is its impeccable handling, thanks to its four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensitive steering. Whether navigating winding roads or cruising the highway, this Honda will provide a confident and composed ride.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Accord's comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including forward collision warning, automatic emergency braking, lane departure warning, and adaptive cruise control. You can rest assured that you and your passengers will be well-protected.

Step inside the Accord's cabin, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy the convenience of the power-adjustable driver's seat with memory function, the warmth of the heated front seats, and the seamless integration of the premium audio system and smartphone connectivity.

This 2017 Honda Accord EX-L is a true standout in the midsize sedan segment, offering a winning combination of style, performance, technology, and safety. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at Floyd Traylor Honda in Fort Smith, AR.

Floyd Traylor Honda in Fort Smith, AR wants to sell you your next car, truck or SUV. We provide new and pre-owned sales, service, parts and financing. Proudly serving northwestern Arkansas and eastern Oklahoma since 1976, we proudly welcome visitors from nearby Fayetteville, Bentonville, Rogers, Springdale, Van Buren, Alma, Poteau, Russellville, Charleston and beyond!

The MP3 player is a convenient feature that takes the sound quality to another level, moreover listening to music from any device with the built-in AUX input makes any road trip exciting. The keyless entry enables you to access your vehicle with ease, meanwhile the installed stability control improves traction on slippery or icy roads.The cruise control takes much of the foot-work out of long distance driving while thanks to the built-in Brake Assist, emergency stopping distances can be shortened, reducing the likelihood of accidents. With this tire pressure monitoring systems, monitoring tire pressure with manual gauges is no longer necessary while the increase in performance from the Dual-Shift transmission delivers a truly exciting driving experience. The power windows are so convenient that it's hard to make do without them, additionally the CD player is a must have for any daily driver.The traction control system is a great safety tool against hydroplaning in snow and rain conditions, moreover the steering wheel audio controls let you control almost every aspect of your music without taking your hands off the wheel.... description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology in this stunning 2017 Chevrolet Malibu LT 1LT. With its sleek gray exterior and well-appointed interior, this midsize sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Highlighted features include:

• Convenience & Technology Package
• Wireless Charging
• 120-Volt Power Outlet
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel and Shift Knob
• Dual USB Charging Ports in Rear
• Color Driver Information Center
• Chevrolet MyLink Radio with 8" Screen

This Malibu LT 1LT is powered by a 1.5L DOHC engine and 6-speed automatic transmission, delivering an impressive 27 city/36 highway MPG. The independent suspension and responsive handling make this Malibu a joy to drive, whether navigating city streets or cruising on the highway.

Safety and convenience are paramount, with features like remote vehicle start, auto-dimming rearview mirror, and an integrated rear-view camera. The Malibu's advanced airbag system, anti-lock brakes, and electronic stability control provide added peace of mind.

Slip into the premium cloth seats and experience the comfort and refinement of this well-equipped Malibu. The driver's seat offers 8-way power adjustability and lumbar support, while the leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob add a touch of elegance.

Chevrolet's MyLink infotainment system, with its 8-inch touchscreen display, seamlessly integrates your compatible smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. Stay connected and entertained on every journey.

With its exceptional fuel efficiency, comprehensive safety features, and impressive technology, this 2017 Chevrolet Malibu LT 1LT is an exceptional value at just $4,000. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of driving this exceptional midsize sedan.

Convenience and safety are also at the forefront, with features like the 8.8" widescreen display, Bluetooth connectivity, heated steering wheel, and a comprehensive suite of driver assistance technologies, including adaptive cruise control, forward collision warning, and lane departure warning.

Whether you're seeking a dynamic daily driver or a captivating weekend companion, the 2017 Alfa Romeo Giulia is a remarkable choice that will exceed your expectations. We invite you to experience the exceptional craftsmanship and performance of this Italian masterpiece. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Giulia should be your next vehicle.

description: Discover the 2017 Honda Civic LX, a sleek and reliable sedan that combines efficiency with everyday practicality. With only 101,507 miles on the odometer, this used Civic offers a smooth ride powered by a 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine producing 158 horsepower at 6,500 RPM and 138 lb-ft of torque at 4,200 RPM. Its front-wheel-drive layout and continuously variable transmission ensure effortless handling and excellent fuel economy, boasting up to 31 mpg in the city and 40 mpg on the highway. The sophisticated gray exterior complements its modern black interior, creating an appealing look that’s perfect for daily commuting or weekend adventures. Equipped with a backup camera and Bluetooth connectivity, this Civic makes driving safer and more convenient, keeping you connected and confident on the road. Designed with driver safety in mind, the 2017 Honda Civic LX features essential security and braking systems. Its ABS with four-wheel disc brakes ensures stable stopping power, even in challenging conditions. Cornering brake control enhances stability during turns, preventing skidding and maintaining control. The vehicle’s auto-locking power door locks add an extra layer of security, automatically securing the doors once you start driving. An electronic parking brake with auto-off functionality simplifies parking maneuvers and enhances safety by automatically disengaging when not in use, reducing driver fatigue and risk. 2017 HONDA CIVIC Safety and Security Features This Civic is equipped with critical safety features including 4-wheel ABS that provides reliable braking performance, cornering brake control that helps maintain stability during turns, auto-locking power door locks to secure the vehicle when in motion, and an electronic parking brake with auto-off that ensures ease of parking and enhances overall safety. 2017 HONDA CIVIC Entertainment and Technology Features Entertainment and connectivity are straightforward with auxiliary audio input via USB, allowing seamless integration with your favorite devices. This feature ensures you stay entertained and connected during your drives, making every trip more enjoyable and convenient.

Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and functionality in this 2017 Honda Civic LX. This sleek and well-appointed sedan is the ideal choice for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, feature-rich vehicle that delivers an exceptional driving experience.

Boasting a striking white exterior, this Civic LX is more than just a pretty face. Under the hood, the 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V i-VTEC engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, provides a responsive and fuel-efficient performance, with an impressive 31 MPG in the city and 40 MPG on the highway.

Key features that set this Civic apart:

• Cruise Control
• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth Connectivity

The well-appointed interior offers a host of thoughtful amenities, including:

• Air Conditioning with Automatic Temperature Control
• Power Windows and Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel-Mounted Audio Controls

The Civic's advanced safety features, such as Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, provide you and your loved ones with the utmost protection on the road.

Beyond its practical advantages, this 2017 Honda Civic LX also delivers a refined and engaging driving experience. The Four-Wheel Independent Suspension, Power Steering, and Traction Control ensure a smooth and responsive ride, while the 16-inch Wheels with Full Covers add a touch of style.

Whether you're commuting to the office, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, this Civic LX is the perfect companion. Its combination of efficiency, technology, and safety make it a standout choice in the compact sedan segment.

We invite you to experience the exceptional value and quality of this 2017 Honda Civic LX. Schedule a test drive today and discover why this vehicle is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance in this 2017 Chevrolet Malibu LT 1LT. Boasting a sleek, modern exterior in a timeless white hue, this midsize sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Equipped with a 1.5L DOHC engine and a 6-speed automatic transmission, the Malibu LT 1LT delivers an impressive fuel efficiency of 27 MPG in the city and 36 MPG on the highway, making it an economical choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

This well-appointed Malibu comes loaded with an array of features to enhance your driving pleasure:

• Cruise Control
• Push Button Start
• USB/AUX Input
• Sirius XM Radio
• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth

The Convenience and Technology Package takes this Malibu to the next level, offering:
• Remote Vehicle Starter System
• Auto-Dimming Rearview Mirror
• 120-Volt Power Outlet
• Color Driver Information Center
• Chevrolet MyLink Radio with 8" Screen
• Wireless Charging
• Dual USB Charging Ports
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel and Shift Knob
• 18" Aluminum Wheels

The Malibu's sophisticated interior boasts premium cloth seating, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a host of advanced safety features, including airbags, anti-lock brakes, and electronic stability control, ensuring your peace of mind on the road.

With its sleek design, impressive efficiency, and comprehensive list of features, this 2017 Chevrolet Malibu LT 1LT is a compelling choice for the discerning driver. We invite you to experience the exceptional quality and value this vehicle has to offer. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover why the Malibu should be your next automotive companion.

Drive City Automotive is proud to offer this 2017 Hyundai ELANTRA SE! With its sleek design and advanced features, this car is sure to turn heads on the road.

But the ELANTRA SE isn't just about looks and comfort. It also comes loaded with technology and safety features to make your driving experience even better. With Bluetooth connectivity, a 7-inch touchscreen display, and a rearview camera, staying connected and in control has never been easier.

And when it comes to safety, the ELANTRA SE has you covered. With features like Blind Spot Detection, Lane Change Assist, and Automatic Emergency Braking, you can drive with peace of mind knowing that you and your passengers are protected.

Don't miss out on your chance to own the 2017 Hyundai ELANTRA SE. Come take a test drive today and experience the ultimate combination of style, performance, and safety. Hurry, this car won't last long!

Discover the exceptional 2017 Jaguar XE 35t R-Sport, a dynamic and refined luxury sedan that seamlessly blends sophisticated style with exhilarating performance. Boasting a striking Ebony exterior and a host of premium features, this XE is poised to elevate your driving experience.

• Black Design Package
• Navigation system: InControl Navigation
• Radio: Meridian 380W Sound System with 11 Speakers
• SIRIUSXM Satellite Radio
• Air Conditioning with Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Power Driver's Seat with Memory Function
• Panoramic Moonroof
• Gloss Black Exterior Accents
• Heated Steering Wheel
• 19" Venom 5 Twin-Spoke Alloy Wheels

Beneath the sculpted hood, the XE 35t R-Sport's 3.0L V6 Supercharged engine delivers a thrilling 340 horsepower, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive for exceptional responsiveness and control. With an EPA-estimated 20 city/29 highway MPG, this Jaguar strikes the perfect balance between power and efficiency.

The cabin of the XE 35t R-Sport surrounds you in premium Taurus Leather upholstery and features a wealth of advanced technology. The InControl Navigation system, Meridian Sound System, and SIRIUSXM Satellite Radio provide seamless connectivity and an immersive audio experience. Dual-zone climate control, heated front seats, and a heated steering wheel ensure your comfort in any weather.

Safety is paramount in the XE 35t R-Sport, which comes equipped with a suite of advanced driver-assistance features. Enjoy the peace of mind of Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keep Assist, Blind Spot Monitoring, and a Rear-View Camera, all working in harmony to help you navigate the road with confidence.

With its striking design, exhilarating performance, and comprehensive suite of premium features, the 2017 Jaguar XE 35t R-Sport is a true standout in the luxury sedan segment. Experience the exceptional for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of Jaguar ownership.

This 2017 Volkswagen Jetta 1.8T SEL, has a Platinum Gray Metallic exterior and an Titan Black interior color. 58,312 miles. Stock Number N25362. Contact our Internet Sales Manager at (775)337-9706. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Year/Make/Model: 2019 Cadillac XTS Trim Level: Premium Luxury Drivetrain: Front-Wheel Drive (FWD) Body Style: Full-Size Luxury Sedan Manufacturing Plant: Oshawa, Ontario, Canada Performance & Engineering The XTS Premium Luxury focuses on effortless power. It features the smooth, naturally aspirated V6 that has been a staple of the Cadillac lineup. Feature Specification Engine 3.6L SIDI DOHC V6 VVT Horsepower 304 hp @ 6,800 rpm Torque 264 lb-ft @ 5,300 rpm Transmission 6-Speed Automatic Brakes Brembo Front Performance Brakes (Standard) Suspension Magnetic Ride Control (Real-time damping) Fuel Economy 19 City/28 Highway/22 Combined mpg Premium Luxury Features The Premium Luxury trim is where Cadillac loaded the XTS with its most advanced technology and comfort features as standard. Magnetic Ride Control: This is the magic of the XTS, it reads the road 1,000 times per second and adjusts the shocks for a perfectly level ride. Lighting: Advanced LED Headlamps with IntelliBeam (automatic high-beam switching) and cornering lamps. Audio: 14-speaker Bose Studio Surround Sound system. Head-Up Display (HUD): A full-color display projecting speed and navigation onto the windshield. Climate: Tri-zone automatic climate control (separate settings for driver, passenger, and rear seats). Interior & Comfort Digital Cockpit: A 12.3-inch reconfigurable gauge cluster (standard on this trim). Seating: Leather-appointed seating with heated and ventilated front seats, plus heated outboard rear seats. Safety Suite: Includes Lane Keep Assist, Lane Departure Warning, Forward Collision Alert, and Safety Alert Seat (vibrates the seat to warn the driver).

With its sleek black exterior, this midsize sedan offers a dynamic and engaging driving experience that will captivate you from the moment you get behind the wheel.

• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Four wheel independent suspension
• ABS brakes
• Dual front impact airbags
• Dual front side impact airbags
• Rear side impact airbag
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Leather Shift Knob
• Sport steering wheel
• Fabric Seat Trim w/SofTex
• Front Bucket Seats
• Split folding rear seat
• Alloy wheels

Powered by a robust 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, this Camry SE delivers an exceptional blend of performance and efficiency, earning an impressive 28 MPG in the city and 39 MPG on the highway. The sport-tuned suspension and precise steering provide a dynamic and engaging driving experience, while the advanced safety features, including the Entune 3.0 Audio system with App Suite, keep you connected and protected on the road.

Step inside the well-appointed interior and you'll be greeted by a host of premium amenities, including a power driver's seat, automatic climate control, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel. The split-folding rear seat and ample cargo space ensure you can easily accommodate your passengers and cargo with ease.

Whether you're commuting to work, embarking on a road trip, or simply enjoying the thrill of the open road, this 2019 Toyota Camry SE is the perfect companion. Experience the exceptional value, style, and performance that this midsize sedan has to offer. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this Camry SE is the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

We are proud to offer this 2019 Toyota Corolla L in Classic Silver Metallic with a Steel Gray interior and 106,286 miles. Options Include: Convenience
  • This \'intelligent\' cruise control system uses laser or radar to maintain a preset following distance behind another vehicle, automatically braking or accelerating as required.
Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
