With its compact size, nimble handling, and responsive steering, you'll be zipping through traffic and taking on corners with ease. Plus, the sleek alloy wheels and sporty design will turn heads wherever you go.Safety is always a top priority, and this Fiesta comes equipped with a range of features to keep you and your loved ones protected. From the antilock brakes to the stability control system, you can drive with confidence knowing that you're in good hands.So why settle for a boring used car when you can have this exciting 2019 Ford Fiesta? With its Carfax report, fuel efficiency, advanced technology, and sporty design, this car has everything you need to make every drive a thrilling experience. Don't wait any longer - come test drive this Fiesta today and see for yourself why it's the perfect car for you! Sporty design meets everyday efficiency in this 2019 Volkswagen Jetta R Line, finished in sleek Platinum Gray Metallic with a Storm Gray and Black premium synthetic interior. Recognized by Kelley Blue Book as one of the 10 Best Sedans Under 30000 and one of the 10 Coolest New Cars Under 20000 when new, the Jetta R Line continues to deliver standout style and value. With mileage below market average, this sedan offers even greater appeal.

Under the hood, the responsive 1.4L TSI turbocharged engine pairs seamlessly with an 8 speed automatic transmission with Tiptronic. This combination provides smooth acceleration, impressive fuel efficiency, and a refined driving experience. Front wheel drive and a well tuned suspension deliver confident handling and comfort whether commuting through town or cruising on the highway.

Inside, the R Line trim adds athletic character with perforated V Tex leatherette seating surfaces, heated front comfort seats, and a leather wrapped shift knob. Dual zone automatic climate control keeps both driver and passenger comfortable, while the power moonroof adds an open, airy feel to the cabin. The Composition Color infotainment system with 6.5 inch touchscreen offers intuitive access to audio and vehicle settings. Steering wheel mounted controls, cruise control, and remote keyless entry enhance daily convenience.

Safety and stability features include a rear view camera, electronic stability control, traction control, ABS brakes, brake assist, multiple airbags, and a tire pressure monitoring system. Exterior details such as front fog lights, fully automatic headlights, and bold 17 inch Trenton alloy wheels complete the distinctive R Line appearance.

This vehicle is not eligible for the Step One Forever Warranty due to model year guidelines. Please ask your sales associate for complete warranty and protection plan details.

Beyond the impressive list of standard features, the Sonata SE offers a smooth, responsive ride thanks to its Four Wheel Independent Suspension and Speed-Sensing Steering. Whether navigating city streets or cruising the highway, this sedan delivers a refined and engaging driving experience.

Discover the perfect balance of style, technology, and performance in the 2019 Hyundai Sonata SE. Visit our showroom today and experience the difference for yourself. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional vehicle and its unbeatable value.

The 2019 Hyundai Sonata SEL offers an exceptional blend of style, comfort, and technology, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver. With its sleek exterior design and well-appointed interior, this sedan is sure to turn heads and provide a truly rewarding driving experience.

• Carpeted Floor Mats

Boasting a powerful 2.4L I4 DGI DOHC 16V engine paired with a 6-Speed Automatic with Shiftronic transmission, the Sonata SEL delivers an impressive 25 city/33 highway MPG, ensuring efficient and enjoyable commutes. The vehicle's front-wheel-drive configuration provides confident handling and a smooth ride, while the four-wheel independent suspension enhances the overall driving dynamics.

Step inside the Sonata SEL and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that prioritizes both comfort and convenience. The heated front bucket seats, dual-zone automatic climate control, and leather-wrapped steering wheel create a premium driving environment, while the advanced infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Sonata SEL boasting a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, a knee airbag, and an emergency communication system. The vehicle also comes equipped with electronic stability control, traction control, and a rearview camera, providing you with added peace of mind on the road.

Experience the exceptional value and refined driving dynamics of the 2019 Hyundai Sonata SEL. With its impressive combination of style, technology, and safety features, this sedan is sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Sonata SEL should be your next automotive purchase.

    Safety and Security
    • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

This 2019 Honda Civic Sedan LX, has a Modern Steel Metallic exterior and Black interior color with only 61,995 miles. Stock Number FU9386. Important Package Information Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.

description:
Feel the wind in your hair and the power of a legend with this breathtaking Cirrus Silver Metallic 2022 Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 55 AMG Roadster. This isn't just a car, it's a high-performance masterpiece designed for those who love the thrill of the open road. With a massive 4.0L V8 engine and the 4MATIC all-wheel drive system, this Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 55 AMG Roadster delivers heart-pounding acceleration while keeping you glued to the pavement. It comes with a clean one-owner CARFAX, meaning its been loved and cared for since day one.

Performance Meets Pure Relaxation
Driving this Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 55 AMG Roadster is an experience like no other. While the V8 engine provides the muscle, the Active Multicontour Front Seats with a Massage Feature make sure you stay relaxed no matter how long the journey. Whether you're carving through mountain curves or cruising down the coast, the adaptive suspension adjusts in real-time to give you the perfect balance of sportiness and comfort. It's the rare kind of vehicle that can be a track-day beast one minute and a serene getaway car the next.

Technology for the Modern Driver
Inside the cabin, you'll find a world of cutting-edge tech that's surprisingly easy to use. This Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 55 AMG Roadster features the MBUX Infotainment system with a beautiful touchscreen that puts your navigation and music front and center. With Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, your favorite playlists and contacts are always just a tap away. The Driver Assistance Package adds a layer of safety with smart features that help you navigate traffic with ease, so you can focus on the pure joy of driving a world-class roadster.

Luxury Built for Every Season
Mercedes-Benz designed this Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 55 AMG Roadster to be enjoyed all year round. Even on cooler days, you can drop the power convertible roof and stay warm thanks to the heated steering wheel and heated seats. The Touring Trim Line ensures the interior is draped in premium Nappa Leather, creating a space that feels incredibly high-end. Little details like the auto-dimming mirrors and rain-sensing wipers handle the small stuff for you, so every trip feels like a special occasion.

A Symphony for Your Ears
When you aren't listening to the roar of the V8 engine, you can immerse yourself in the Burmester Surround Sound System. Its specifically tuned to sound amazing even when the top is down, providing a crisp and powerful audio experience. This Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 55 AMG Roadster truly offers the best of everything: timeless style, incredible power, and the kind of luxury that only an AMG can provide. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of automotive history that's ready for its next adventure.

*Burmester is a registered trademark of Burmester Audiosysteme GmbH, Berlin, Germany. *Bluetooth is a registered mark of Bluetooth SIG, Inc.

With an original MSRP of $187,400, this 2022 Mercedes-AMG SL 63 represents the pinnacle of open-air performance, luxury, and cutting-edge engineering. Finished in exclusive Moonlight White Magno, a $3,250 upgrade, the matte exterior accentuates the SLs sculpted lines and aggressive AMG stance, delivering a striking and unmistakable presence.

The interior is appointed with premium Black Nappa leather accented by red stitching, a $1,900 upgrade that creates a bold, performance-focused cockpit. The Performance Trim Line, originally priced at $1,800, further enhances the cabin with AMG-specific detailing that reinforces the vehicles motorsport heritage. Heated and ventilated front seats provide year-round comfort, while massaging front seats elevate long-distance driving to a first-class experience.

Engineered for both performance and everyday usability, this SL 63 is equipped with a front axle lift system to assist when navigating steep driveways or speed bumps. Rolling on 20-inch AMG twin five-spoke wheels, it maintains a confident balance of athleticism and refinement. The Burmester premium sound system delivers rich, immersive audio, while Apple CarPlay ensures seamless smartphone integration for navigation, communication, and entertainment. A rearview camera adds confidence during low-speed maneuvering. Combining breathtaking performance, handcrafted luxury, and advanced technology, this 2022 Mercedes-AMG SL 63 stands as an exceptional grand touring roadster for the most discerning drivers.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 63 AMG® 4MATIC®. This meticulously maintained, one-owner vehicle boasts a stunning white exterior and a host of premium features that will captivate your senses.

• Mercedes-Benz Factory Certified
• 1 Owner**
• Sold New Here
• Driver Assistance Package

Beneath the sleek and aerodynamic design, this SL-Class is powered by a potent 4.0L V8 engine paired with a smooth-shifting 9-Speed Automatic transmission and the confidence-inspiring 4MATIC® all-wheel-drive system. With an impressive 14 city/21 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of performance and efficiency.

This Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned vehicle comes with a comprehensive suite of benefits that provide unparalleled peace of mind:

• 165+ Point Inspection
• Roadside Assistance
• Warranty Deductible: $0
• Transferable Warranty
• Vehicle History
• Limited Warranty: 12 Month/Unlimited Mile beginning after new car warranty expires or from certified purchase date

Step inside and experience the epitome of luxury and technology. The cabin is adorned with premium Nappa Leather upholstery, heated and ventilated front seats, and the cutting-edge MBUX Infotainment & Navigation System. Immerse yourself in the rich, 3D Surround Sound provided by the Burmester® High-End audio system.

This SL 63 AMG® 4MATIC® also comes equipped with a wealth of advanced safety features, including the Driver Assistance Package, which includes innovative technologies like Adaptive Cruise Control, Active Blind Spot Assist, and more, ensuring your driving experience is not only thrilling but also secure.

Elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures with this exceptional 2022 Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 63 AMG® 4MATIC®. Schedule a test drive today and discover the unparalleled performance, luxury, and craftsmanship that this certified pre-owned masterpiece has to offer. Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned means you get an additional 12 months Limited Warranty on top of the existing factory warranty, with unlimited mileage. We also do up to a 162-point rigorous inspection/reconditioning, 24/7 roadside assistance, trip-interruption services, and a complete CARFAX vehicle history report. Comes with 12 Month/Unlimited Mile warranty + Trip Interruption Reimbursement and 7 days/500 miles Exchange Privilege

Thank you for choosing Butler Toyota of Jacksonville, this Suzuka Gray Metallic/Black Roof 2015 Audi R8 V8 is a great choice! Check out the following: No Accidents! City 14/Hwy 23 Audi Exclusive Black Optic Package ($1,200 value)
  • High-Gloss Black Round Exhaust Pipes
  • 235/35 91Y 19 Front and 305/30R19 102Y Rear Tires
  • 19\' 5-Double Spoke Titanium Design Wheels
Full Leather Package ($5,500 value)
  • Fine Nappa Leather Seat Trim
Comfort
  • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
Convenience
  • Cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, an integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. With integrated navigation system you always know the right way.
Don't miss out, come see us at 1290 Cassat Ave Jacksonville FL 32205 or call us at and schedule a test drive today! Family Owned since 1970. Butler Toyota Jacksonville provides you with the ultimate new, used, and certified pre-owned car buying experience in Florida! Our hardworking team of qualified sales, service, and finance specialists strive to bring you an overall superior car buying experience from beginning to end. We will help you find the perfect new, used, or certified pre-owned Toyota that meets all of your needs and desires, and will work alongside you to come up with a finance plan that accommodates your lifestyle. In addition, we provide our valued customers with a fantastic service department that will keep your vehicle running smoothly for years to come. If you are in the Jacksonville, Jacksonville Beach or Orange Park area, come check out all of the outstanding vehicles and services at Butler Toyota Jacksonville, FL!

Thank you for visiting another one of Mercedes-Benz of Sarasota's online listings! Please continue for more information on this 2025 M4 Competition with 2,224mi. With its full CARFAX one-owner history report, you'll know exactly what you are getting with this well-kept BMW M4. The M4 Competition is a well-built, yet compact and enjoyable ride that is unmatched by any other convertible on the road. With the ability to easily switch between having the top up or down, you'll be able to go about your weekday routine without feeling like you've sacrificed the weekend thrills. There's a level of quality and refinement in this M4 Competition that you won't find in your average vehicle. When driving an all wheel drive vehicle, such as this M4 Competition, superior acceleration, traction, and control come standard. Intricately stitched leather and ergonomic design seats are among the details in which test drivers say that BMW M4 Competition is in a league of its own Drive any city's streets like you've lived there all your life using the navigation system on this BMW M4. If not for a few miles on the odometer you would be hard-pressed to know this 2025 BMW M4 is a pre-owned vehicle. This rare vehicle is a prime example of automotive engineering perfected.

description:
Introducing the 2025 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 3LT - a true masterpiece of engineering and design. This stunning sports car boasts a thrilling 6.2L V8 engine, paired with an 8-speed dual clutch transmission and rear-wheel drive, delivering an exhilarating driving experience like no other.

Highlighted features include:

• One Owner
• Clean Carfax
• Z51 Performance Package
• Front Lift Adjustable Height with Memory
• 19" x 8.5" Front and 20" x 11" Rear 20-Spoke Bright Machined-Face Forged Aluminum Wheels
• Body-Color High Wing Spoiler
• Bright Red-Painted Calipers
• Custom Leather Wrapped Interior Package
• Memory Driver & Passenger Convenience Package
• Preferred Equipment Group 3LT

But the true standout features of this Corvette Stingray are the ones that elevate it to a level of unparalleled performance and luxury. The Navigation System, Convertible Hardtop, and Bose Performance Series Sound System with 14 Speakers provide the perfect blend of technology and entertainment. The Head-Up Display and Electronic Limited-Slip Differential take the driving experience to new heights, while the Z51 Performance Brakes and Suspension ensure you can harness every ounce of power with precision and control.

Comfort and convenience are also key, with features like Heated and Vented Seats, a Heated Steering Wheel, and Wireless Charging for your devices. The Sueded Microfiber-Wrapped Upper Interior Trim Package adds a touch of elegance, while the Rear Cross Traffic Alert and Side Blind Zone Alert provide added peace of mind on the road.

This 2025 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 3LT is a true masterpiece, blending exceptional performance, cutting-edge technology, and uncompromising luxury. With its stunning Red exterior and just 1,455 miles on the odometer, this vehicle is a rare find that won't last long. Experience the thrill of owning a true American icon - schedule your test drive today and discover the power and passion of the Corvette Stingray.

Introducing the captivating 2025 BMW 4 Series M440i xDrive, a true masterpiece of German engineering. This stunning vehicle boasts a powerful 3.0L I6 engine, paired with an 8-Speed Automatic Sport transmission and BMW's renowned xDrive all-wheel-drive system, delivering an exhilarating driving experience like no other.

The exterior of this M440i xDrive is adorned in a sleek and sophisticated White color, complemented by the Shadowline Package that adds a touch of sportiness with its M Sport Brakes, M Shadowline Lights, and more. Step inside, and you'll be enveloped in the luxurious Vernasca Leather upholstery, with the Premium Package providing the ultimate in comfort and convenience, including the stunning BMW Curved Display with Head-Up Display and the renowned harman/kardon Surround Sound System.

The Driving Assistance Package takes your driving experience to new heights, with features like Active Cruise Control and Automatic Pull-Away, ensuring your journeys are both thrilling and effortless. The Parking Assistance Package, on the other hand, makes maneuvering a breeze, with Active Park Distance Control, Surround View with 3D View, and the Parking Assistant Plus.

This BMW 4 Series M440i xDrive is not just a vehicle – it's a statement of refined performance and uncompromising luxury. With its impressive fuel efficiency, delivering 25 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, this car is as practical as it is exhilarating to drive.

As a BMW Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this M440i xDrive has been meticulously inspected and comes with the peace of mind of an extended warranty, ensuring you can enjoy the ultimate driving experience with confidence. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional vehicle your own.

description:
One owner, Clean Carfax! This 2025 BMW 840i xDrive Convertible looks incredible in Black Sapphire Metallic with Black Extended Merino Leather. It has a strong 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-6 engine, 8-speed Sport Automatic transmission, and xDrive all-wheel drive. Its set up for better handling with Integral Active Steering and M Sport brakes with blue calipers, sitting on 19-inch M Double-spoke wheels.

The cabin is packed with options, including the Driving Assistance Package with Active Park Distance Control, Parking Assistant Plus, and a 3D Surround View camera. For comfort, you have heated front seats, heated armrests, and a heated steering wheelperfect for top-down driving. You also get soft-close automatic doors and Remote Engine Start. Tech features include Live Cockpit Pro with navigation, a Head-Up Display, and Harman Kardon Surround Sound. This is a loaded convertible ready for a new home at Jeff's Motorcars.

Safety and Security
  • Night vision - Lift the veil of darkness. We've all been there, it's dark, and suddenly something appears out of nowhere in the road! With this safety feature, the night no longer holds unpleasant surprises. Working in combination with the headlights, night vision uses infrared technology to detect obstacles in the dark and show them on your display screen. Night vision makes for a safer drive between dusk and dawn.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.

description:
This 2017 Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 550 in timeless elegance combines high-performance engineering with refined luxury, offering an unmatched driving experience. Powered by a 4.7L V8 BiTurbo engine paired with a 9-speed automatic transmission, this rear-wheel-drive SL 550 delivers smooth, responsive acceleration and effortless cruising. With low mileage2,559 miles below market average its practically like new, ready to thrill its next owner.

Inside, the cabin is a showcase of craftsmanship and comfort. Leather upholstery and Burl Walnut Wood Trim provide a sophisticated aesthetic, while ventilated front seats and power-adjustable seats ensure a personalized and comfortable ride. The auto tilt-away steering wheel improves accessibility, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls put entertainment at your fingertips. Center console storage adds practicality to the luxurious interior.

This SL 550 is equipped with advanced safety and driver assistance technologies, including Active Blind Spot Assist, Active Lane Keeping Assist, DISTRONIC PLUS with Steering Assist, DISTRONIC PLUS with Pre-Safe Brake, PRE-SAFE PLUS, and Speed Limit Assist, all designed to keep you confident and protected on every drive. Driver Assistance Package and ParkAssist (Front and Rear) make parking and maneuvering effortless, while the glass rear window adds style and visibility.

The exterior exudes Mercedes-Benz elegance and sportiness, featuring 19 AMG 5-Spoke Wheels, signature badging on the dashboard, and a sleek, aerodynamic design. Combined with remote keyless entry, this SL 550 is as convenient as it is commanding.

Blending performance, technology, and luxury, this 2017 Mercedes-Benz SL-Class SL 550 is a perfect choice for drivers seeking the exhilaration of a high-powered roadster with the sophistication and comfort Mercedes-Benz is renowned for.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2020 Mercedes-Benz E-Class E 450. Boasting a sleek blue exterior, this luxury sedan combines exceptional performance and refined elegance, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Beneath the hood, you'll find a powerful 3.0L V6 BiTurbo engine mated to a smooth 9-Speed Automatic transmission, delivering an exhilarating driving experience. With a fuel-efficient 20 city/27 highway MPG rating, this E-Class offers the perfect balance of power and efficiency.

This E 450 is equipped with an impressive array of features, including:

• AMG® Line Package
• Warmth & Comfort Package
• AMG® Bodystyling
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Heated & Active Ventilated Front Seats
• Burmester® Surround Sound System
• Navigation System
• Apple CarPlay®/Android Auto®

The AMG® Line Package adds a touch of sportiness with its distinctive styling cues, while the Warmth & Comfort Package ensures you and your passengers enjoy a cozy and luxurious driving experience, even on the coldest days.

Step inside the cabin and you'll be greeted by a stunning interior, featuring genuine wood accents and premium leather upholstery. The power-adjustable front seats with memory function provide exceptional comfort and support, while the Burmester® Surround Sound System delivers an immersive audio experience.

With its advanced safety features, including a rearview camera, blind spot monitoring, and a suite of airbags, this E-Class prioritizes your well-being on the road. The intuitive COMAND® infotainment system and seamless smartphone integration via Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto® keep you connected and in control.

This 2020 Mercedes-Benz E-Class E 450 is a true testament to the brand's commitment to craftsmanship, performance, and luxury. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident this exceptional vehicle will exceed your expectations and leave a lasting impression.

description: Just arrived is this stylish and luxurious, NO-ACCIDENT, ONE-OWNER, NONSMOKER 2025 Mercedes-Benz CLE 300 4MATIC Cabriolet with ALL-WHEEL DRIVE! ''There aren't many luxury drop-tops left anymore, but the 2025 Mercedes-Benz CLE Cabriolet proves they are still worth getting. Its quiet and refined ride left us impressed, and its savvy top-down features will entice you to drop the top. The CLE Cabriolet shares most of its qualities with its coupe counterpart, and that's a good thing. If you're looking for a luxury cruiser that offers sun-on-your-face smiles, you won't be disappointed with the CLE Cabriolet,'' Edmunds writes. Key Accolades & Recognition: Edmunds Expert Rating: Highlighted smooth ride, good handling for its size, and strong performance, especially the CLE 450 4MATIC. U.S. News & World Report: Noted it's a well-rounded convertible with advanced tech, though it hasn't been crash-tested yet. MotorTrend Reviews: Praised the CLE Cabriolet as a ''carefully thought-out convertible that overflows with appeal,'' noting its posh interior, tech, and comfort-meets-sportiness. The Car Expert Awards (2025): Featured as a strong contender in their ''Best Convertible 2025,'' acknowledging its elegance and comfort. Why It's Noteworthy: Successor & Standalone: It fills the gap left by the C-Class and E-Class coupes/convertibles, becoming Mercedes' primary 2-door luxury convertible. Performance & Comfort: Offers a blend of strong performance (especially the 450 model) with the expected plush Mercedes ride quality and useful convertible technology (like heat management). Strong Reliability: J.D. Power predicts ''Great'' reliability for the 2025 model. So far, it is receiving widespread positive reviews for its design, luxury, and overall execution as a modern convertible. With its odometer now hovering around the 3,617 mark, it is STILL COVERED under the balance of the New Vehicle Limited Warranty until May 2029 or 50,000 miles (whichever occurs first)! Yes, the 2025 Mercedes-Benz CLE 300 4MATIC Cabriolet is a mild-hybrid vehicle, featuring a 2.0L turbocharged 4-cylinder engine paired with a 48-volt Integrated Starter-Generator (ISG) for electric assist, smoother start/stop, and improved efficiency, but it's not a plug-in hybrid (PHEV). It delivers 255 hp, comes standard with 4MATIC all-wheel drive, and offers luxury features like the AIRSCARF neck-level heating for top-down comfort. The CLE 300 coupe and convertible offer the following standard features: LED headlights and taillights Power tilt-and-telescoping steering wheel Heated front seats with memory settings 12.3-inch digital instrument cluster 11.9-inch infotainment touchscreen Navigation system 17-speaker Burmester premium audio system Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smartphone connectivity Wireless device charging Fingerprint sensor (configures preferred settings for up to seven drivers for seats, audio, climate and other systems) Neck-warming seat vent (convertible model only) Priding itself on 'The Best or Nothing,' it commits to excellence with: AMG LINE PACKAGE AMG Bodystyling AMG Line Exterior AMG Line Interior MB-Tex Dashboard with Nappa Look Sport Brake System Sporty Engine Sound NIGHT PACKAGE High-Gloss Black Elements -inc: high-gloss black elements: front wing, grille lamellas, rear diffuser insert and exterior mirrors Wheels: 19'' AMG Multispoke Black Metallic Paint Heated Steering Wheel ...and you can certainly bet there's a bunch more! You can view vehicle files above this description [on our site], which may include the original brochure and window sticker! Please note that in November 2025 Mercedes-Benz USA reacquired this vehicle due to customer complaints in regards to what was only described as a 'windows/windshield concern.' Mercedes-Benz made all the necessary repairs and adjustments under warranty to fully resolve all specified concerns, however they agreed to repurchase the vehicle to promote customer satisfaction. We have all the documentation from Mercedes-Benz USA on file. BUY WITH CONFIDENCE AS THE FACTORY WARRANTY IS STILL INTACT! This is an exceptional opportunity to take this one home, don't hesitate or you will surely miss out! SAVE THOUSANDS off retail pricing with this magnificent condition 2025 Mercedes-Benz CLE! We will happily size up TRADE-IN OFFERS and have EXCELLENT FINANCE OPTIONS as well, so please give us a call at 732-919-0707 (Wall Township) or 856-881-2869 (Sewell) TODAY!

The 2015 Chevrolet Corvette 2dr Stingray Z51 Conv w/3LT, draped in a striking Shark Gray Metallic exterior, epitomizes the blend of performance and elegance. Inside, the Kalahari interior provides a warm and inviting contrast, creating a cabin environment that's both luxurious and comfortable. Powered by a formidable 6.2L V8 engine, this Corvette offers an exhilarating driving experience that is synonymous with the legendary Corvette name. Enhancing its allure, the vehicle includes the coveted 3LT preferred equipment group, providing amenities that elevate the driving experience to a superior level of convenience and sophistication. The Atlantic Design Package adds an exclusive touch, further distinguishing this model on the road. The sporty aesthetic is accentuated by LPO Z51-style satin black aluminum wheels featuring a bold red stripe, sized at 19 inches in the front and 20 inches in the rear. For those seeking added personalization, the customer-selectable VIN ending offers a unique touch of individuality. Additionally, the availability of LPO torque directional chrome aluminum wheels at the same sizing ensures versatility in styling options. Together, these features encapsulate a Corvette that is both an icon of American performance engineering and a statement piece for any automotive enthusiast. With its perfect marriage of style, comfort, and raw power, this Stingray Z51 assures a captivating and exhilarating drive every time you get behind the wheel. description:
At Miracle Autosport, we believe in providing a transparent, no-hassle car buying experience. As a one-price dealership, we list our best price online with no surprise negotiations. We re proud of our reputation:
  • 4.5+ Stars across all major review platforms
  • A+ Rating with the Better Business Bureau
  • CarGurus Top Rated Seller for the last 4 years
Our FeesAll vehicles are subject to a $695 document fee and a $199 preparation fee, that s it! No hidden charges or surprises.Our Process
Each of our vehicles undergoes a thorough inspection, including a 5-10 mile test drive, to ensure everything is in top condition. Any issues we identify are addressed prior to sale whether it s replacing tires or brakes that are below 50% of their usable life, resolving any suspension noises or vibrations, or repairing any damages beyond normal wear and tear. While we can't predict the future, we take every measure to ensure your vehicle is as smooth, reliable, and hassle-free as possible.Now, let's dive into the details of the vehicle you're interested in below.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2008 Bentley Continental GTC Convertible One-Owner | 54,710 Miles | Dark Sapphire Blue/Saffron Leather/Blue TopHere s your chance to own a true grand-touring icon. This one-owner since new Bentley Continental GTC shows just 54,710 miles and is finished in stunning Dark Sapphire Blue over Saffron leather, topped off with a Blue power convertible roof. Clean Carfax, non-smoker owned, and clearly loved its entire life.This GTC runs and drives beautifully, looks absolutely stunning inside and out, and everything works exactly as it should no warning lights, no surprises. Powered by Bentley s twin-turbo W12 and all-wheel drive, it delivers effortless speed with proper British luxury.?? Inspection & MaintenanceAs with every vehicle we sell, this Bentley underwent a thorough test drive and detailed inspection by Miracle Autosport s service department.
  • Brakes are in great shape
  • Excellent matching set of Pirelli tires
  • All wear-and-tear items found to be well within proper spec
Two small cosmetic items were noted and are already being handled:
  • A crack in the passenger mirror housing (being replaced)
  • Light wear on the driver seat bolster (our interior specialist is correcting this)
Updated photos will be uploaded once completed. Miracle Autosport ensures each car offered for sale is in the best shape possible.? Standout Features & Factory Options (with original pricing)Originally stickered at $204,065, this GTC was nicely optioned from the factory:
  • Birds Eye Maple Veneer $890
  • 20 7-Spoke Painted Alloy Sport Wheels $3,540
  • 3-Spoke Two-Tone Leather-Wrapped Sport Steering Wheel $2,500
  • Drilled Alloy Sport Foot Pedals $640
  • Sporting Gear Lever in Knurled Chrome & Leather $640
  • Front & Rear Deep Pile Carpet Mats w/Leather Trimming $440
  • Valet Parking Key $290
  • Privacy Handset $340
  • Original Shipping Charge $795
Plus desirable factory selections including:
  • Dark Sapphire exterior paint
  • Blue convertible top
  • Saffron leather interior with matching headliner
  • Saffron secondary trim (seat belts & carpeting)
And of course the GTC essentials: AWD, adaptive air suspension, bi-xenon headlights, navigation, heated memory seats, premium audio, park sensors, power everything, and that glorious W12 soundtrack.?? ConditionDrives very nicely. Very clean interior. Non-smoker owned. Body is in beautiful condition, wheels present well, and the car feels exactly how a Bentley should tight, smooth, and quietly fast. Interior leather and wood trim show extremely well, and once the minor cosmetic touch-ups are completed, this will be a truly standout example.? ClosingFinding a one-owner, clean Carfax Continental GTC in this color combo and condition is getting harder every year. This is a properly cared-for, well-optioned convertible Bentley that s ready to be enjoyed immediately.Miracle Autosport CarGurus Top Rated Seller (last 4 years) and top rated on all respected dealer review sites. We inspect, we drive, we care so you just drive and grin.CLICK HERE FOR NEW CAR WINDOW STICKER!

Most of our vehicles qualify for up to 60 month/100k mile service contracts. If you are interested in a quote, please just ask!

Our document fee of $695 covers all internal costs to facilitate the deal, any other additional charges may include state taxes, tags, title fees, and out-of-state title agent costs.

Our team is not commission based so you can speak to anyone at the dealership without any feeling of stepping on the toes of your salesperson. All of us are friends in and out of work and we are a profit-sharing company, so everyone here works as a team to keep our clients happy and our inventory fresh!

We are available to answer questions 7 days a week. You can reach us by voice or text at 609-552-0711 during business hours and we watch for texts/inquiries in the evenings until 9:30 EST.

We are a brick-and-mortar dealership established in 2005 and are about to begin a total renovation of our showroom and service department which will also include a driver's lounge for our clients to come to watch races and take part in weekend drives with us. We maintain over 4-star reviews on CarGurus, Carfax, and Google. We also have over 1,300 positive feedback ratings on eBay so you can buy with confidence.

Give us a call or text at 609-552-0711 so we can answer any questions you might have!

description: "Must See" New arrival, this 2017 Mercedes-Benz SL 450 blends timeless roadster design with modern luxury and exhilarating performance. Powered by a smooth and responsive twin-turbo V6, the SL 450 delivers effortless acceleration and confident handling, enhanced by adaptive air suspension that provides a refined, composed ride in any driving mode. The iconic power-folding hardtop transforms this SL from a sleek coupe into an open-air convertible at the touch of a button, letting you enjoy top-down driving without sacrificing comfort or cargo space.The interior is finished in rich Oyster leather with Burl Walnut wood trim and showcases Mercedes-Benz craftsmanship at its finest. Premium I Package features include heated and active ventilated front seats with massage, the AIRSCARF neck-level heating system for comfortable top-down driving, KEYLESS-GO, hands-free trunk access, and PARKTRONIC with Active Parking Assist and rearview camera. The Driver Assistance Package adds cutting-edge safety and convenience with DISTRONIC PLUS adaptive cruise control with steering assist, PRE-SAFE braking and PRE-SAFE Plus, active blind spot monitoring, active lane keeping assist, and speed limit assist for added confidence on every drive.Technology is seamlessly integrated with the COMAND navigation system, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, and a harman/kardon Logic 7 surround sound system that delivers immersive audio quality. With its elegant design, thrilling performance, and a cabin that exemplifies luxury and refinement, this SL 450 offers an exceptional grand touring experience that stands apart from ordinary convertibles.

5.0L V8 POWER -- VELOCITY BLUE CONVERTIBLE FUN -- B&O SOUND -- ADAPTIVE CRUISE -- LANE KEEPING -- MAGNERIDE SUSPENSION -- BLIND SPOT ALERT -- HEATED & COOLED LEATHER SEATS

The 2020 Ford Mustang GT Premium Convertible in head-turning Velocity Blue Metallic with a striking Showstopper Red interior redefines open-air driving. Feel the thrill as you grip the 6-speed manual transmission, engaging every horsepower from the commanding 5.0L V8 Ti-VCT engine. The GT Performance Package, with its MagneRide Damping System and larger brake rotors, ensures you're carving corners with daring precision.

Slide into the luxurious interior where premium meets innovation. Leather bucket seats with color accents underline your comfort, with climate-controlled heating and cooling to match any weather. You'll appreciate the power adjustability that tailors to your perfect driving position, while the heated steering wheel and aluminum instrument panel create an atmosphere of elegant performance.

Stay seamlessly connected and entertained on every drive with the SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System. Accompanied by the brilliant B&O Sound System by Bang & Olufsen, your favorite tunes will soar through 9 speakers, transforming every road trip into a concert. Navigate confidently with voice-activated touchscreen navigation and enjoy the convenience of steering wheel-mounted audio controls.

Safety and innovation are seamlessly integrated with the Ford Safe & Smart Package. Navigate your days with confidence thanks to Adaptive Cruise Control, while the Lane-Keeping System and Blind Spot Information System with Cross-Traffic Alert have your back on bustling highways. The Pre-Collision Assist features ensure extra peace of mind for every journey.

Drop the top and embrace the lifestyle that this sporty convertible complements so well. Whether it's prowling city streets or cruising coastal highways, this Mustang's active valve performance exhaust roars with approval. It's not just a drive, it's an expression of freedom and thrill.

Visit Guntersville Chevrolet today to experience this Mustang GT Premium Convertible in person. Our commitment to exceptional customer service and transparent pricing makes your purchase journey as exhilarating as the car itself. We are proud to offer this 2025 Mazda MX-5 Miata Grand Touring in Machine Gray Metallic with Black interior and offers 26 city/35 highway mpg. CarFax No Accidents! CarFax One Owner! We're a proud member of the Ken Harvey Auto Group, which means we're one of several family-owned and family-operated dealerships. We realize that our success depends upon your satisfaction and has for decades. Here at Dublin Mazda, we strive to provide our customers with welcoming, convenient and genuine experiences. From the vehicle purchasing process to servicing your Mazda, it is our mission to make you feel like family. Mazda Certified Pre-Owned Details:* 160 Point Inspection* Transferable Warranty* Powertrain Limited Warranty: 84 Month/100,000 Mile (whichever comes first) from original in-service date* Vehicle History* Limited Warranty: 12 Month/12,000 Mile (whichever comes first) after new car warranty expires or from certified purchase date* Warranty Deductible: $0* Includes Autocheck Vehicle History Report with 3 Year Buyback Protection. 3 month SiriusXM trial subscription.* Roadside Assistance Our goal is to have the biggest selection of Used Mazdas in Northern California. But it's all about quality, so we keep only the finest trade-ins and get rid of the rest, which means you're always picking from the best. And with Mazda booming in popularity, we get lots of non-Mazda trade-ins, too. Regardless of brand, every used car we offer comes with the Ken Harvey Advantage, your guarantee of quality. Popular Options and Features Include: Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Android Auto/Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description: Black, Perforated Sensatec Upholstery, Heated Steering Wheel, Premium Package, Remote Engine Start, Skyscraper Grey Metallic, Wheels: 18'' X 7.5'' V-Spoke Bicolor. Our fun-to-drive One Owner 2025 BMW 4 Series 430i xDrive Convertible with the Premium Pack in Skyscraper Grey Metallic surrounds you with open-air elegance, refined comfort, and all-weather assurance. Motivated by a TurboCharged 2.0 Liter TwinPower 4 Cylinder supplying 255hp to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission for acceleration with exhilaration. This All Wheel Drive convertible also carves through the curves with sport-focused handling, achieving nearly 33mpg on the highway. Striking design cues help our 4 Series turn heads with impressive aerodynamics, a power soft top, LED lighting, Shadowline trim, alloy wheels, and a bold interpretation of the classic BMW kidney grille. People expect more from our 430i cabin, and they can find it. The inviting interior boasts remote start, SensaTec power heated front sport seats, a leather-wrapped heated sport steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, cruise control, ambient lighting, Fine Wood Oak Grain trim, and rewarding technologies. Your digital benefits extend to the 8.8-inch touchscreen, 5.1-inch driver display, full-color navigation, WiFi compatibility, Apple CarPlay®, Bluetooth®, and a Hi-Fi audio system. For safety's sake, BMW supplies advanced driver assistance from automatic braking, forward collision warning, a rearview camera, active blind-spot monitoring, lane-departure warning, dynamic stability/traction control, and more. Now unlock our 430i xDrive convertible and get underway with style and strength! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership! . Discover unmatched choice at Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh, home to a huge lineup of new vehicles and one of the largest used-car inventories on the east coast with 1,000+ options ready to drive.

• Convertible HardTop
• MAZDA CONNECT Infotainment system
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• AppLink/Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Heated front seats
• Alloy wheels

Prepare to experience the iconic Mazda MX-5 Miata RF Club, a true driver's delight that effortlessly blends performance, style, and open-air exhilaration. This 2025 model, with just 5,042 miles, is a rare find, offering the perfect balance of power, precision, and pure driving pleasure.

Beneath the sleek, sculpted exterior lies the heart of a true sports car – a potent 2.0L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine mated to a smooth-shifting 6-speed manual transmission. With 26 city/34 highway mpg, this Miata RF delivers an unparalleled combination of spirited performance and exceptional fuel efficiency, ensuring you can maximize the thrill of the open road without breaking the bank.

Step inside the cabin and you'll be greeted by a host of premium features that elevate the driving experience. The Nappa leather upholstery with Alcantara inserts, heated Recaro sport seats, and leather-wrapped steering wheel create an inviting and supportive environment, while the MAZDA CONNECT infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained.

Handling is where the Miata RF truly shines, thanks to its lightweight, balanced chassis and precise, responsive steering. The 17-inch BBS forged dark gunmetal finish alloy wheels wrapped in high-performance tires provide exceptional grip and agility, allowing you to carve through corners with confidence and precision.

Whether you're seeking the thrill of open-air driving or the convenience of a retractable hardtop, the 2025 Mazda MX-5 Miata RF Club delivers an unparalleled driving experience. Discover the true essence of the Miata legacy and unleash your passion for the road.

Choose Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh, NC for a dealership experience built on transparency, value, and customer-first service. With a wide selection of new CJDR models and an extensive inventory of quality used cars, trucks, and SUVs, Westgate is a trusted destination for shoppers across Raleigh, Durham, the Triangle and all of North Carolina.

Every vehicle at Westgate comes pre-installed with Recovr vehicle location technology and professional window tint, included for a total cost of $799.

description:
Unleash your inner thrill-seeker with the 2025 Ford Mustang EcoBoost Premium, a stunning convertible that perfectly blends power and style. With its sleek Carbonized Gray Metallic exterior and luxurious Black Onyx leather seating, this Mustang is designed to turn heads wherever you go. Under the hood, the robust 2.3L 4-cylinder engine delivers an exhilarating 315 horsepower, ensuring that every drive is a heart-pounding adventure. Packed with cutting-edge technology, including Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, a back-up camera, and dual-zone climate control, this Mustang offers both comfort and connectivity. With only 4,922 miles on the odometer, this one-owner vehicle is ready to hit the road. Don't miss your chance to experience the thrill of driving a Mustang—come in for a test drive today!

This Mustang EcoBoost Premium comes equipped with an impressive array of features, including Lane Departure Warning, Bluetooth connectivity, keyless entry, Sirius Satellite Radio, and premium wheels. Enjoy the convenience of heated seats, power mirrors, and lumbar support, all designed to enhance your driving experience. Safety is paramount with side airbags and a tire pressure monitoring system, ensuring peace of mind on every journey.

description: Just arrived is this sleek and luxurious, ONE-OWNER, NONSMOKER 2025 BMW Z4 sDrive30i Roadster! Offering sheer driving pleasure, this luxury sports car ''strikes a nice balance between hard-charging performance and luxury cruising. Comfort and style are definite highlights, as are relative cargo space and fuel efficiency,'' as U.S. News writes. Key Awards & Recognition: CarBuzz Favorite: Named a favorite car of 2025 by CarBuzz, highlighting its unexpected delight and strong performance. BMW Blog Favorite: Featured as one of the ''Best BMWs of 2025,'' with the manual M40i praised as the ''best BMW sports car of 2025'' by some editors. With us, it's not a simple purchase, it's a white-glove, elevated experience.Welcome to The Platinum Collection - where luxury meets unparalleled service in the world of exotic, unique, high-end vehicles. As a distinguished family-owned dealership & showroom, we are dedicated to crafting an exceptional experience for our clientele. Our state-of-the-art showroom serves as a sanctuary for those seeking the finest selection of the world's most coveted automotive marques. In addition to our prestigious automotive offerings, we also proudly present our exclusive, high-end watch collection embodying sophistication and elegance.Our meticulously curated inventory features over one hundred of the most sought-after brands, including: Lamborghini, Rolls-Royce, Rolex, Bentley, Breitling, Ferrari, Richard Mille, Aston Martin, Patek Philippe, McLaren, Audemars Piguet, Mercedes-Benz and so much more.All of our inventory goes though a rigorous inspection process to ensure the highest quality. At The Platinum Collection, we understand that acquiring a luxury vehicle or timepiece transcends mere transaction, it is an experience to be cherished. Our knowledgeable and dedicated team is committed to providing personalized service, guiding you through every detail of your journey, and ensuring that your experience with us is nothing short of extraordinary.VEHICLE DESCRIPTION:2013 Mercedes-Benz SL550, Roadster 2DIf you seek a true luxury grand-tourer that can play quiet and classy or twin-turbo V8 missile, this SL550 nails it. This example is finished in a timeless Black on Black combo and pairs a power-retractable hardtop (with Magic Sky Control glass) with a seriously comfortable, tech-forward cabin.
  • Mileage: ~69,097 miles
  • Color combo: Black exterior/Black interior
  • Title: reported Clean (FL)
  • Location history: reported Florida-owned from new, Carfax referenced in auction listing
  • Premium 1 Package: heated/ventilated active seats w/massage, AIRSCARF, Parktronic w/Active Parking Assist, power trunk closer, Keyless-GO
  • Driver Assistance Package: Distronic Plus radar cruise, Active Blind Spot Assist, Active Lane Keeping Assist
  • Magic Sky Control hardtop glass panel + Harman Kardon audio + AMG exterior styling + adaptive bi-xenon headlights
  • Aftermarket HRE wheels (aggressive, modern multi-spoke design)
  • Continental tires (SportPlus branding visible)
  • Black leather interior with wood trim accents throughout the cabin
  • Wood/leather steering wheel for a premium, classic feel
  • Aluminum speaker grilles (premium audio look + feel)
  • Signature SL styling: long hood, wide stance, and that timeless Mercedes roadster profile
This isn t a little convertible. The SL550 is built to be a high-speed cruiser quiet and comfortable when you want it, and seriously responsive when you lean into the throttle. Safety and Security
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will.
